25|$|In 1869, the Paiute Wodziwob founded <b>the</b> <b>Ghost</b> <b>Dance</b> movement. The dance rituals were an {{occasion}} {{to announce his}} visions of an earthquake that would swallow the whites. He seems to have died in 1872.|$|E
