50|$|Several ditonic {{scales were}} noted about the Modoc and Klamath tribes of the North American West Coast, {{and are also}} found in the Great Plains in the rituals of <b>the</b> 1800s <b>Ghost</b> <b>Dance</b> religion. <b>The</b> scale was also used in the music of the Shawnee.|$|R
