50|$|In 1996, Beggars Banquet remastered and reissued the 1988 eponymous Death Cult compact disc. This new {{collection}} {{was released in}} the UK and US simultaneously (marking the first time Death Cult material was released in the US). The compact disc collection featured new artwork and was given <b>the</b> title <b>Ghost</b> <b>Dance.</b>|$|R
